### Dependency Scope Execution Flow

Source: https://github.com/fastapi/fastapi/blob/master/docs/en/docs/tutorial/dependencies/dependencies-with-yield.md

Illustrates the sequence of execution for dependencies with 'request' and 'function' scopes, showing when setup and teardown (after yield) code runs relative to the path operation.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram

participant client as Client
participant dep_req as Dep scope="request"
participant dep_func as Dep scope="function"
participant operation as Path Operation

    client ->> dep_req: Start request
    Note over dep_req: Run code up to yield
    dep_req ->> dep_func: Pass dependency
    Note over dep_func: Run code up to yield
    dep_func ->> operation: Run path operation with dependency
    operation ->> dep_func: Return from path operation
    Note over dep_func: Run code after yield
    Note over dep_func: ✅ Dependency closed
    dep_func ->> client: Send response to client
    Note over client: Response sent
    Note over dep_req: Run code after yield
    Note over dep_req: ✅ Dependency closed
```

